FITNESS (feat. Coach Brennan - @brenpkelly)
⁣
I knew that fitness was a key component of health, but I didn’t know how to do it well. When I met Brennan in Hawaii, I had no idea where I would be a year later.⁣
⁣
I had fitness goals and he had a system to help achieve them. ⁣
⁣
The goals included:⁣
💪🏽 Reach 180 lbs, tapping into self care
💪🏽 Increase energy levels⁣ with routine strength training
💪🏽 Improve dieting habits⁣, aiding in mental clarity 
⁣
With that said, it wasn’t just physical. I needed holistic help, coping with new life stressors and anxieties.⁣
⁣
So, here is my progress after a year and counting… ⁣
⁣
I want to thank Brennan for his guidance, friendship, and accountability.⁣
⁣
This guy is doing some phenomenal work (check out his page). I had to brag on him.⁣ 
⁣
Love you bro! 🤍
